snippet.title: Selena Gomez, Amber Heard, Miranda Kerr Dazzle on the Red Carpet!
snippet.description:
Like Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/therealalist 
Follow Twitter - http://www.twitter.com/therealalist
More A-List videos - http://ow.ly/6lEM2

All the best photos from the red-carpet events of the past two weeks! Which celebrities have played it cool and who's just looked a fool?! Featuring Selena Gomez, J-Lo, Jessica Alba, Johnny Depp and more!


AFI FEST 2011 
LA, November 3-10

04 Johnny Depp, Amber Heard
05 Eva Green
 
MTV Europe Music Awards
Belfast, November 6
 
01 LMFAO
02 Jessie J
03 Selena Gomez
04 JWOWW + Snooki
05 David Hasselhoff
 
Glamour's 2011 Women Of The Year Awards
NYC, November 7
 
01 Cindi Leive, Jennifer Lopez and Donatella Versace
02 Jessica Alba
02 Emma Stone
03 Jennifer Lopez 

Victoria's Secret Fashion Show
NYC , November 9
 
01 Kanye West, Izabel Goulart
02 Adriana Lima
03 Alessandra Ambrosio
04 La La Vazquez
05 Miranda Kerr

45th Annual CMA Awards
Nashville, November 9
 
01 Taylor Swift
02 Nicole Kidman, Keith Urban
03 Ginnifer Goodwin
04 LeAnn Rimes
05 Lionel Richie
 
Fashion Fail Runner up
 
30 Seconds to Mars (MTV EMAs)
 
Fashion Fail Winner:
 
LMFAO (MTV EMAs)
